{"tid":603272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"15歲女啓晴邨慘遭污辱　70歲補習老師被控強姦","createTime":"2018-03-23T15:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T15:32:30.000Z","uid":5195,"like":26,"dislike":270,"uniUserReply":113,"replies":[{"pid":"f71bce1ee03987d91960dde252c44e6a43975037","tid":603272,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"九龍啟德啟晴邨發生強姦案，一名15歲少女慘受污辱，警方拘捕一名70歲老翁，他已被暫控強姦，將於明日應訊。據了解，15歲少女於本周二(20日)晚上在啟晴邨一單位內，被姓林70歲補習老師強姦。少女不甘受辱，於是向家人傾訴。家人聞悉後大驚，翌日立即報警求助。秀茂坪警區重案組第一隊經調查後，同日在牛頭角以涉嫌強姦拘捕涉案老翁，並已暫控他一項強姦罪，案件於明日(24日)在東區裁判法院提堂。據了解，被捕男子為補習老師，受害少女到其家中上課時慘被性侵。"},{"pid":"83fd30a29b87625bb9ff716c8a3ddd357b4e7609","tid":603272,"uid":67500,"like":532,"dislike":17,"score":515,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"老而彌堅"},{"pid":"bb65288d03b8c2872b98f6e9b1e5459f9c355640","tid":603272,"uid":52276,"like":9,"dislike":24,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:10:36.000Z","msg":"支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a3ba00287c40269caf8e1655062419d7233b84","tid":603272,"uid":103207,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:10:57.000Z","msg":"鉛水村"},{"pid":"92276ab26c508b7652314cc069b4b2836336b95c","tid":603272,"uid":113178,"like":43,"dislike":3,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:10:59.000Z","msg":"好慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21864eba36e070e11e9d3d81b9c8ad578de9b66","tid":603272,"uid":118120,"like":5,"dislike":33,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:11:02.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"8955e07629fd5553f2b775fac541ebe1978ad8cf","tid":603272,"uid":26451,"like":13,"dislike":73,"score":-60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:11:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2603bccdfb7b93d51c98e3bc4f0ab99bd6fe503","tid":603272,"uid":162103,"like":754,"dislike":3,"score":751,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"70歲補習老師????????????"},{"pid":"74d8a8a09e53761a3021de05ce